# ==============================================================================
# The scammers want your passwords for cloud/mail/webmail accounts.
# You'll be asked to:
# - Check a password
# - Renew your service
# - Increase a limit.
#
# So we have company names from the IT sector here like:
# - Cloud Storage
# - EMail Services
# - Hosting
# - Domains
# - Office
#
# Additionally, we are including AI service providers here.
# The criminals want to renew the subscription.
#
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Language: english
# Weight:   12.0
# ==============================================================================

# Topics
# ==============================================================================

# TLD in front, usualy (ch|com|de|org)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
/\.[a-z]{1,4}.{1,5}storage.{1,10}almost full/i

